wiki.summary: "GATÚBELA" (Spanish for "Catwoman") is a song by Colombian singer-songwriter Karol G and Puerto Rican rapper Maldy. It was written by Giraldo, Maldy, Justin Quiles, Lenny Tavárez and Marvin Hawkins and produced by the latter and Giraldo. The song was released on August 25, 2022 through Universal Music Latino, as the second single from her fourth studio album, Mañana Será Bonito. The song was announced a day prior to its release through Karol G's social media platforms with the title, release date and a clip of the music video. Read more on Last.fm.
